00:25:44.440 --> 00:25:45.119
Xiaoling,

00:25:46.079 --> 00:25:47.160
let me add one more thing.

00:25:48.880 --> 00:25:49.839
Now that your husband

00:25:49.839 --> 00:25:51.200
is investigating you,

00:25:51.759 --> 00:25:53.319
why aren't you divorcing him?

