Let me help you, okay?

00:26:10.880 --> 00:26:11.759
How long will you

00:26:11.839 --> 00:26:12.680
keep struggling?

00:26:12.799 --> 00:26:13.680
Thank you, Zhang Ye.

00:26:14.720 --> 00:26:15.599
But I want to give

00:26:15.640 --> 00:26:16.480
myself some time.

00:26:17.376 --> 00:26:19.599
(Talking with a classmate.
Meet at the café tomorrow.)

