I'm not delaying.

00:26:24.000 --> 00:26:25.559
I just want to be certain.

00:26:25.880 --> 00:26:26.319
Fine.

00:26:28.079 --> 00:26:28.680
Be certain.

00:26:29.640 --> 00:26:31.000
When you've been certain,

00:26:31.039 --> 00:26:31.880
come find me.

