Add me again, okay?

00:26:40.599 --> 00:26:41.200
I'll scan you.

00:26:49.279 --> 00:26:50.240
Well, your wife

00:26:50.440 --> 00:26:51.519
appears completely alone

00:26:51.599 --> 00:26:52.720
with no signs of cheating.

