Polishing is one
of the most charming parts

00:29:26.000 --> 00:29:27.400
in ceramic making.

00:29:28.039 --> 00:29:29.799
Layer by layer,

00:29:30.359 --> 00:29:31.440
all the bumps,

00:29:31.519 --> 00:29:32.799
uneven flaws

00:29:32.960 --> 00:29:34.200
and wrinkles

00:29:34.519 --> 00:29:35.839
are smoothed out

00:29:36.160 --> 00:29:37.119
in this process,

00:29:37.960 --> 00:29:39.759
making it closer and closer
to perfection.

00:29:41.240 --> 00:29:42.440
Do you think it's boring?

00:29:44.480 --> 00:29:45.559
I often

00:29:46.359 --> 00:29:47.880
exfoliate and remove dead skin too.

00:29:51.000 --> 00:29:52.200
If polishing life

00:29:53.400 --> 00:29:54.640
could be simple as exfoliating,

00:29:54.640 --> 00:29:55.680
that'd be great.

00:29:56.960 --> 00:29:57.519
Right.

00:29:57.880 --> 00:29:58.720
Master Zeng

00:29:58.799 --> 00:30:00.480
can't even tolerate blemish flaws,

00:30:01.000 --> 00:30:02.279
how could you not meticulously

00:30:02.279 --> 00:30:03.720
polish your own life?

00:30:05.400 --> 00:30:07.240
If you keep polishing like this,

00:30:07.759 --> 00:30:09.079
will you polish me away too?

00:30:11.079 --> 00:30:12.279
What nonsense are you talking?

00:30:12.880 --> 00:30:13.839
You know exactly

00:30:13.920 --> 00:30:14.920
how I care about you.

00:30:19.200 --> 00:30:20.319
You care about me

00:30:20.839 --> 00:30:22.200
because I don't care about you.

00:30:22.599 --> 00:30:23.920
I don't want to marry you

00:30:24.319 --> 00:30:25.799
or spend eternity with you.

00:30:26.640 --> 00:30:27.599
That's how people are.

00:30:28.319 --> 00:30:30.119
They don't learn
until they pay the price.

00:30:31.960 --> 00:30:33.480
Just like my dad and mom.

00:30:34.599 --> 00:30:35.920
Even after years of divorce,

00:30:36.680 --> 00:30:38.240
they still only care about themselves.

00:30:39.680 --> 00:30:40.640
How do you get along?

00:30:41.319 --> 00:30:41.920
Get along?

00:30:52.319 --> 00:30:53.200
I know she's acting.

00:30:53.880 --> 00:30:55.279
She knows I know she's acting.

00:30:55.440 --> 00:30:56.440
She knows I'm acting.

00:30:56.640 --> 00:30:57.960
I know she knows I'm acting.

00:30:58.240 --> 00:30:59.079
So we both just

00:30:59.400 --> 00:31:00.400
keep up our own acts,

00:31:00.920 --> 00:31:02.599
fully aware of each other's performance.

00:31:05.559 --> 00:31:06.640
I often wonder

00:31:07.279 --> 00:31:08.279
if our marriage

00:31:09.440 --> 00:31:11.279
is an exception

00:31:12.279 --> 00:31:13.480
or just like most others.

00:31:17.240 --> 00:31:18.000
I don't know

00:31:18.039 --> 00:31:18.920
what marriage is like.

00:31:19.559 --> 00:31:20.640
And I don't want to know.

00:31:22.319 --> 00:31:23.119
But your marriage

00:31:23.160 --> 00:31:24.400
is already at stake.

00:31:24.880 --> 00:31:26.000
Have you thought of leaving?

00:31:29.359 --> 00:31:31.119
This marriage hasn't brought me

00:31:31.359 --> 00:31:32.079
much happiness,

00:31:32.799 --> 00:31:33.839
but it's not painful.

00:31:34.720 --> 00:31:35.400
It's not

00:31:35.519 --> 00:31:37.160
the best time to end it now.

00:31:37.839 --> 00:31:38.559
Besides,

00:31:39.559 --> 00:31:40.200
it hasn't become

00:31:40.240 --> 00:31:40.960
an obstacle yet.

00:31:42.160 --> 00:31:42.839
Otherwise,

00:31:43.680 --> 00:31:44.759
I wouldn't ignore it.

00:31:52.319 --> 00:31:53.039
Master Zeng,

00:31:53.559 --> 00:31:54.759
you keep polishing.

00:31:55.240 --> 00:31:56.359
I'll hang out with friends,

00:31:56.440 --> 00:31:57.440
not being with you today.

00:31:57.440 --> 00:31:57.920
Bye-bye.

00:32:35.519 --> 00:32:36.640
Stop drinking.

00:32:37.400 --> 00:32:39.279
The doctor said you can't drink.

00:32:42.279 --> 00:32:43.200
Where did all the money

00:32:43.839 --> 00:32:44.359
come from?

00:32:44.720 --> 00:32:45.960
I worked at a gallery.

00:32:46.599 --> 00:32:47.440
150 per piece.

00:32:47.880 --> 00:32:48.759
I made 2,000 of them.

00:32:52.720 --> 00:32:53.920
When you were ten,

00:32:54.720 --> 00:32:56.119
I went to the city with villagers

00:32:57.000 --> 00:32:58.319
to look for jobs.

00:32:59.640 --> 00:33:01.200
A townsman's uncle

00:33:01.519 --> 00:33:02.279
was the foreman.

00:33:02.640 --> 00:33:05.640
He took us to do renovation jobs.

00:33:06.240 --> 00:33:07.640
I did that job for over a decade.

00:33:08.079 --> 00:33:08.880
Otherwise,

00:33:09.519 --> 00:33:11.319
I couldn't afford your education.

00:33:13.039 --> 00:33:13.640
Sit.

00:33:20.200 --> 00:33:21.079
Back then,

00:33:21.359 --> 00:33:22.960
when renovating homes,

00:33:23.680 --> 00:33:24.720
the foreman taught us

00:33:25.039 --> 00:33:27.880
how to judge if a boss is decent.

00:33:28.680 --> 00:33:30.359
If they come to the site,

00:33:30.720 --> 00:33:32.799
bringing us drinks or snacks,

00:33:33.039 --> 00:33:34.640
and greet us first,

00:33:35.319 --> 00:33:37.480
saying "Good work",

00:33:38.359 --> 00:33:39.200
they're good people.

00:33:41.680 --> 00:33:43.839
Those who come empty-handed

00:33:44.119 --> 00:33:46.279
and boss us around

00:33:47.039 --> 00:33:48.200
while constantly complaining

00:33:48.279 --> 00:33:50.000
about everything

00:33:51.359 --> 00:33:52.720
are bad people.

00:33:54.480 --> 00:33:56.160
With good people,

00:33:57.000 --> 00:33:58.279
work would be easier.

00:33:59.559 --> 00:34:01.359
Just do the basics right.

00:34:01.799 --> 00:34:03.400
If they want changes,

00:34:04.039 --> 00:34:05.160
we can drag it out

00:34:05.519 --> 00:34:06.920
to earn extra days' pay.

00:34:08.199 --> 00:34:09.719
With bad people,

00:34:10.280 --> 00:34:11.960
you must work meticulously.

00:34:12.840 --> 00:34:13.679
Do it poorly,

00:34:14.199 --> 00:34:15.159
and they'll replace

00:34:15.480 --> 00:34:16.440
the whole crew.

00:34:17.039 --> 00:34:18.960
They'll argue over your pay and never

00:34:19.159 --> 00:34:19.800
give it to you.

00:34:20.920 --> 00:34:22.320
After all these years,

00:34:23.440 --> 00:34:25.320
I've learned just one thing.

00:34:27.920 --> 00:34:29.960
Nice guys finish last.

00:34:32.679 --> 00:34:33.559
Son,

00:34:34.719 --> 00:34:37.119
those old sayings hold truth.

00:34:38.679 --> 00:34:39.679
I carried buckets

00:34:39.920 --> 00:34:41.079
up and down ladders,

00:34:41.280 --> 00:34:42.920
painting walls for over a decade.

00:34:43.480 --> 00:34:44.440
And I kept wondering

00:34:45.400 --> 00:34:47.199
why city folks

00:34:48.159 --> 00:34:49.880
get to live in such big houses,

00:34:51.320 --> 00:34:53.559
while we only paint walls for others.

00:34:57.159 --> 00:34:58.400
It never made sense to me.

00:34:59.559 --> 00:35:00.719
Never.

00:35:02.039 --> 00:35:02.880
The foreman said

00:35:03.679 --> 00:35:04.760
people should accept fate.

00:35:05.840 --> 00:35:06.760
I accepted it.

00:35:07.519 --> 00:35:10.519
This is what my life will always be.

00:35:12.599 --> 00:35:13.440
Son,

00:35:17.360 --> 00:35:19.119
you're different.

00:35:21.440 --> 00:35:22.760
You've made it

00:35:23.599 --> 00:35:24.639
to university,

00:35:25.719 --> 00:35:27.440
and are about to start graduate school.

00:35:28.760 --> 00:35:30.039
You'll settle in the city

00:35:30.639 --> 00:35:32.000
and change your fate.

00:35:32.480 --> 00:35:33.119
If you succeed,

00:35:33.519 --> 00:35:34.360
my years

00:35:34.400 --> 00:35:35.519
of painting walls

00:35:38.760 --> 00:35:39.800
would be worth it.

00:35:48.639 --> 00:35:50.400
Lin Fang

00:35:51.920 --> 00:35:53.320
is a good wife.

00:35:54.440 --> 00:35:55.920
I'm very satisfied with her.

00:35:56.880 --> 00:35:58.079
She is thrifty,

00:35:58.320 --> 00:35:59.480
respectful to elders,

00:35:59.800 --> 00:36:01.039
and never complains.

00:36:02.159 --> 00:36:03.599
She is such a good wife.

00:36:04.960 --> 00:36:05.800
What a pity.

00:36:08.719 --> 00:36:10.880
Feelings can't be forced.

00:36:15.480 --> 00:36:16.079
Son,

00:36:16.159 --> 00:36:17.000
remember.

00:36:18.360 --> 00:36:19.679
Since ancient times,

00:36:20.360 --> 00:36:21.599
marriage

00:36:22.760 --> 00:36:24.480
has always been a lifelong commitment.

00:36:25.400 --> 00:36:27.440
Don't hold her back.

00:36:29.800 --> 00:36:30.760
You're educated

00:36:31.159 --> 00:36:32.199
and know more than I do.

00:36:33.360 --> 00:36:33.960
But

00:36:34.760 --> 00:36:35.599
there's one thing

00:36:36.519 --> 00:36:37.880
I need to tell you.

00:36:39.159 --> 00:36:40.760
Whatever you do,

00:36:41.760 --> 00:36:43.199
don't hesitate.

00:36:43.679 --> 00:36:44.559
Just do it.

00:36:45.760 --> 00:36:46.360
Don't overthink

00:36:46.679 --> 00:36:47.960
about anything else.

00:36:48.320 --> 00:36:50.119
You just move forward with all efforts.

00:36:50.960 --> 00:36:51.920
If anyone blocks you,

00:36:52.400 --> 00:36:53.400
compete with them.

00:36:55.039 --> 00:36:56.000
We scare nothing.

00:36:58.199 --> 00:36:59.840
I get it, Dad.

00:37:01.519 --> 00:37:02.639
So do you know

00:37:03.920 --> 00:37:06.039
who's blocking you now?

00:37:06.639 --> 00:37:07.320
Who?

00:37:11.840 --> 00:37:12.800
Me.

00:37:14.840 --> 00:37:15.719
Look.

00:37:16.800 --> 00:37:18.199
You want to treat me

00:37:18.360 --> 00:37:19.320
and get more money.

00:37:20.039 --> 00:37:21.840
It's all holding you back.

00:37:22.639 --> 00:37:24.719
You're my dad.

00:37:25.320 --> 00:37:26.239
So what if I am?

00:37:26.719 --> 00:37:27.679
Not even your dad.

00:37:29.320 --> 00:37:30.239
Listen carefully.

00:37:31.440 --> 00:37:32.239
Stop treating me.

00:37:33.239 --> 00:37:34.599
What's the point of being cured?

00:37:35.000 --> 00:37:36.719
I'd still be a cripple.

00:37:37.079 --> 00:37:38.280
Except for spending money,

00:37:38.519 --> 00:37:39.360
what else can I do?

00:37:39.960 --> 00:37:41.639
I'm a burden to you.

00:37:42.960 --> 00:37:44.400
If you're truly filial,

00:37:44.880 --> 00:37:47.000
find me a peaceful way

00:37:47.320 --> 00:37:48.039
and let me die.

00:37:48.920 --> 00:37:49.599
Otherwise,

00:37:50.519 --> 00:37:51.760
I'll drink paraquat.

00:37:52.039 --> 00:37:53.320
Dad, listen to me.

00:37:53.480 --> 00:37:54.079
Did you

00:37:54.119 --> 00:37:55.039
hear what I said?

00:37:59.199 --> 00:38:00.800
Don't give the money to your mom,

00:38:01.760 --> 00:38:03.440
or use it to build a house back home.

00:38:04.599 --> 00:38:06.239
Every penny should be spent

00:38:06.320 --> 00:38:07.480
where it truly matters.

00:38:08.159 --> 00:38:10.000
Consider these things carefully.

00:38:12.159 --> 00:38:13.280
Be grateful

00:38:13.599 --> 00:38:14.480
to your teachers

00:38:16.119 --> 00:38:17.360
and superiors.

00:38:19.320 --> 00:38:20.400
